      <title>下周数据显示德国经济衰退将对欧洲造成压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/german-recession-seen-weighing-on-europe-in-next-week-s-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国经济轻微衰退给欧元区带来压力，且欧元区通胀率温和回升，可能会引发下周欧元区一系列强劲数据的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/german-recession-seen-weighing-on-europe-in-next-week-s-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 15:44:22 GMT</pubDate>
