    <item>
      <title>华尔街找到了另一种解决税收和损失的办法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-25/wall-street-finds-another-workaround-with-taxes-losses-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的贾斯蒂娜·李 (Justina Lee) 解释了华尔街如何采用一种被称为“税收意识多空”的策略——帮助客户押注某些股票，而押注其他股票，这种做法几乎可以确保损失可以用作税收减免。她在“彭博未平仓合约”上发言。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-25/wall-street-finds-another-workaround-with-taxes-losses-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 15:42:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
